<div id="Item_0" class="PageTitle"><div class="Options"></div><h1>SUCCESSFUL - Baker Company Campaign - Operation Neptune (D-Day)</h1></div>

<div id="Discussion_1828" class="Item ItemDiscussion">
    <div class="Discussion">
        <div class="Item-Header DiscussionHeader">
